      "type": "Term",
      "front": "Enforcement Acts",
      "back": "Cruikshank, the Court gutted the Enforcement Acts by throwing out the convictions of some of those responsible for the Colfax Massacre of 1873.",
      "hint": "Cruikshank, the Court gutted the Enforcement Acts by throwing out the convictions of some of those responsible for the Colfax Massacre of 1873.",
      "imageId": null,
