      "type": "Term",
      "front": "Civil Rights Act of 1875",
      "back": "Before the new Congress met, the old one enacted a final piece of Reconstruction legislation, the Civil Rights Act of 1875.",
      "hint": "Before the new Congress met, the old one enacted a final piece of Reconstruction legislation, the Civil Rights Act of 1875.",
